[section#atomics.general
    [:en] General
    [:zh_CN] 综述
]

[para]
[:en] Let [`[^COPYCV](FROM, TO)] be an alias for type [`TO]
with the addition of [`FROM][=']s top-level cv-qualifiers.
[:zh_CN] 令 [`[^COPYCV](FROM, TO)] 为类型 [`TO] 添加 [`FROM] 的顶层 cv 限定符后的别名。

[para]
[:en] Subclause [#atomics] describes components for fine-grained atomic access.
[:zh_CN] 子条款 [#atomics] 描述提供细粒度的原子性访问的组件。

[:en] This access is provided via operations on atomic objects.
[:zh_CN] 这种访问是通过原子性对象的各种操作来提供的。
